('chapters-qld', 'Queensland Chapters', '<p>Queensland chapters connect riders across the state with regular rides, events, and support.</p><div class="card"><img src="/uploads/about/about-chapters-hero.jpg" alt="Queensland riders" style="width:100%; border-radius:8px; margin-bottom:1rem;"><h3>Queensland</h3><p>Chapter representatives can help you connect with local rides and events.</p></div><div class="grid grid-3 chapter-grid"><div class="card"><img src="/uploads/about/committee-placeholder.png" alt="Greg Naylor" style="width:100%; border-radius:8px; margin-bottom:0.75rem;"><h3>Brisbane Chapter</h3><p>Greg Naylor</p><p><a href="tel:0410256667">0410 256 667</a></p><p><a href="mailto:ar.brisbane@goldwing.org.au">ar.brisbane@goldwing.org.au</a></p></div><div class="card"><img src="/uploads/about/committee-placeholder.png" alt="Robert \'86\' Watson" style="width:100%; border-radius:8px; margin-bottom:0.75rem;"><h3>Fraser Coast Chapter</h3><p>Robert \'86\' Watson</p><p><a href="tel:0400112012">0400 112 012</a></p><p><a href="mailto:ar.frasercoast@goldwing.org.au">ar.frasercoast@goldwing.org.au</a></p></div></div>', 'public', NOW()),
('chapters-wa', 'Western Australia Chapters', '<p>Western Australia chapters coordinate local rides and keep members connected across the state.</p><div class="card"><img src="/uploads/about/about-chapters-hero.jpg" alt="Western Australia riders" style="width:100%; border-radius:8px; margin-bottom:1rem;"><h3>Western Australia</h3><p>Chapter representatives can help you connect with local rides and events.</p></div><div class="grid grid-3 chapter-grid"><div class="card"><img src="/uploads/about/committee-placeholder.png" alt="David Goodchild" style="width:100%; border-radius:8px; margin-bottom:0.75rem;"><h3>Perth Chapter</h3><p>David Goodchild</p><p><a href="tel:0417987742">0417 987 742</a></p><p><a href="mailto:ar.perth@goldwing.org.au">ar.perth@goldwing.org.au</a></p></div><div class="card"><img src="/uploads/about/committee-placeholder.png" alt="Gary Cubbage" style="width:100%; border-radius:8px; margin-bottom:0.75rem;"><h3>West Coast Wings Chapter</h3><p>Gary Cubbage</p><p><a href="tel:0407447159">0407 447 159</a></p><p><a href="mailto:ar.westcoastwings@goldwing.org.au">ar.westcoastwings@goldwing.org.au</a></p></div></div>', 'public', NOW()),
('chapters-sa', 'South Australia Chapters', '<p>South Australian riders connect through a dedicated chapter and local events.</p><div class="card"><img src="/uploads/about/about-chapters-hero.jpg" alt="South Australia riders" style="width:100%; border-radius:8px; margin-bottom:1rem;"><h3>South Australia</h3><p>Chapter representatives can help you connect with local rides and events.</p></div><div class="grid grid-3 chapter-grid"><div class="card"><img src="/uploads/about/committee-placeholder.png" alt="Colin Underhill" style="width:100%; border-radius:8px; margin-bottom:0.75rem;"><h3>South Australian Chapter</h3><p>Colin Underhill</p><p><a href="tel:0421357116">0421 357 116</a></p><p><a href="mailto:ar.southaustralian@goldwing.org.au">ar.southaustralian@goldwing.org.au</a></p></div></div>', 'public', NOW()),
('chapters-tas', 'Tasmania Chapters', '<p>Tasmanian members stay connected through local rides and chapter support.</p><div class="card"><img src="/uploads/about/about-chapters-hero.jpg" alt="Tasmania riders" style="width:100%; border-radius:8px; margin-bottom:1rem;"><h3>Tasmania</h3><p>Chapter representatives can help you connect with local rides and events.</p></div><div class="grid grid-3 chapter-grid"><div class="card"><img src="/uploads/about/committee-placeholder.png" alt="Dennis Davis (Contact)" style="width:100%; border-radius:8px; margin-bottom:0.75rem;"><h3>Tasmania Chapter</h3><p>Dennis Davis (Contact)</p><p><a href="tel:0429351615">0429 351 615</a></p><p><a href="mailto:ar.tasmania@goldwing.org.au">ar.tasmania@goldwing.org.au</a></p></div></div>', 'public', NOW()),
('chapters-vic', 'Victoria Chapters', '<p>There is currently no local chapter in Victoria. Please contact the National President.</p><div class="card"><img src="/uploads/about/about-chapters-hero.jpg" alt="Victoria riders" style="width:100%; border-radius:8px; margin-bottom:1rem;"><h3>Victoria</h3><p>Chapter representatives can help you connect with local rides and events.</p></div><div class="card"><p>No local chapter yet. Contact the National President.</p><p><a href="tel:0429324426">0429 324 426</a><br><a href="mailto:aga.president@goldwing.org.au">aga.president@goldwing.org.au</a></p></div>', 'public', NOW()),
('chapters-nt', 'Northern Territory Chapters', '<p>There is currently no local chapter in the Northern Territory. Please contact the National President.</p><div class="card"><img src="/uploads/about/about-chapters-hero.jpg" alt="Northern Territory riders" style="width:100%; border-radius:8px; margin-bottom:1rem;"><h3>Northern Territory</h3><p>Chapter representatives can help you connect with local rides and events.</p></div><div class="card"><p>No local chapter yet. Contact the National President.</p><p><a href="tel:0429324426">0429 324 426</a><br><a href="mailto:aga.president@goldwing.org.au">aga.president@goldwing.org.au</a></p></div>', 'public', NOW()),
('constitution', 'Constitution', '<p>The Constitution outlines membership, governance, and committee responsibilities for the association.</p><div class="card"><h3>Download the Constitution</h3><p>Use the link below to view the latest version. If it does not download, contact the committee.</p><p><a class="button primary" href="/uploads/about/constitution.pdf">Download PDF</a></p></div>', 'public', NOW()),
('presidents-address', 'Presidents Address', '<div class="grid grid-3"><div class="card"><img src="/uploads/about/committee-lewis-furner.webp" alt="Lewis Furner" style="width:100%; border-radius:8px; margin-bottom:0.75rem;"><h3>Lewis Furner</h3><p>National President</p></div><div class="card"><h3>Welcome from the President</h3><p>Hello and welcome to the Australian Goldwing Association. The AGA is a group of like minded Goldwing enthusiasts from Australia and New Zealand who come together monthly for rides and functions. We hold our Annual General Meeting in various locations around Australia each year.</p><p>I joined the AGA in 2007 and have held the positions of Area Rep in the ACT and ST Chapter, Quartermaster for a couple of years and Area Rep in the Riverina Chapter. I took on the President position at the AGA AGM held at Stanthorpe in Qld in 2023.</p><p>I live on a farm 50 km north east of Wagga Wagga in NSW. Although I am retired, I help out my brother and his son as required. The busiest time for me on the farm is during the main shearing in July, and harvest in November and December.</p><p>Take a look around our website and get to know us. Hopefully we will see you as a member and in person soon.</p><p>President, Lewis Furner</p><p>aga.president@goldwing.org.au</p><p>0429 324 426</p></div></div>', 'public', NOW()),
('agm', 'Annual General Meeting', '<p>The Australian Goldwing Association Annual General Meeting is a favorite among members. Financial members are encouraged to attend to help set direction and elect new committee members, with a full weekend of rides and social events.</p><div class="grid grid-3"><div class="card"><h3>Hundreds of riders</h3><p>This event gathers riders from across the country for connection and community.</p></div><div class="card"><h3>Three day event</h3><p>We come together for a three day event, sharing stories, catching up with old friends, and finishing with the AGM dinner.</p></div><div class="card"><h3>Hosted across Australia</h3><p>The AGM location changes each year so every region can participate.</p></div></div><div class="grid grid-3"><div class="card"><img src="/uploads/about/agm-hero.jpg" alt="AGM riders" style="width:100%; border-radius:8px; margin-bottom:0.75rem;"><p>Recent AGM moments</p></div><div class="card"><img src="/uploads/about/agm-dinner.jpg" alt="AGM dinner" style="width:100%; border-radius:8px; margin-bottom:0.75rem;"><p>Celebrations and awards</p></div></div><p>Other events during the year include chapter meetings, inter chapter rides, camping weekends, charity rides, maintenance days, and social rides.</p>', 'public', NOW());
